            <category term="poetry"/>
            <category term="nature"/>

        <updated>2026-05-24T13:34:00-07:00</updated>
            <summary type="html">
                <![CDATA[
                        <img src="https://www.jujubemonster.com/media/posts/105/EL5uR.jpg" alt="" />
                    I do not know what gorgeous thing The bluebird keeps saying, His voice easing out of his throat, beak, body into the pink air of the early morning. I like it whatever it is. — Mary Oliver
                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                    <p><img src="https://www.jujubemonster.com/media/posts/105/EL5uR.jpg" class="type:primaryImage" alt="" /></p>
                <p class="wp-block-paragraph">I do not know what gorgeous thing<br>The bluebird keeps saying,<br>His voice easing out of his throat,<br>beak, body into the pink air<br>of the early morning.  I like it<br>whatever it is. </p>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">— Mary Oliver</p>
